LlamaXML v1.0.1 (wiz3D vendor drop)
Original code by Llamagraphics, Inc.

NOTE ON THE wiz3D DROP
----------------------
The headers under Include/LlamaXML/ are the LlamaXML public API surface
as released by Llamagraphics under GPL v2.

The binaries under lib/{x86,x64}/ were produced from an in-tree wiz3D
implementation (src/LlamaXML.cpp under lib/LlamaXML/ in the parent
repo). That .cpp is a deliberate rewrite -- not a copy of the upstream
LlamaXML source. It implements the subset of the LlamaXML API actually
used by wiz3D (XMLReader, XMLWriter, FileInputStream, FileOutputStream,
TextEncoding, XMLException), and owes nothing line-by-line to the
upstream source.

Because the headers retain the upstream license, this drop is shipped
under the upstream GPL v2 terms. A future pass intends to replace the
headers with a clean reimplementation so the whole drop can move to
wiz3D's LGPL 2.1 baseline; until that lands, this directory is ambiguously
licensed as GPL v2.

